tyle="position: absolute;"><div class="slider" style="position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; height: 10px; transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px); contain: strict;"></div></div><div role="presentation" aria-hidden="true" class="invisible scrollbar vertical" style="position: absolute;"><div class="slider" style="position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; width: 10px; transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px); contain: strict;"></div></div><div class="shadow"></div><div class="shadow"></div><div class="shadow"></div></div></div></div></div><div class=".in-cell-overflowing"><div widgetid="editor.contrib.quickInputWidget" style="position: absolute; top: 0px; right: 50%;"></div></div></div></div></div>
        <div class="text-top-div">
          <div class="markdown"><span><div class="text-cell-section-header layout horizontal center"><md-icon-button class="header-section-toggle" title="Свернуть 0 дочерних ячеек в разделе &quot;Executive Conclusions &amp; Insights&quot; (чтобы свернуть ячейки и в других разделах этого уровня, также нажмите &lt;Shift&gt;)" data-aria-label="Свернуть 0 дочерних ячеек в разделе &quot;Executive Conclusions &amp; Insights&quot; (чтобы свернуть ячейки и в других разделах этого уровня, также нажмите &lt;Shift&gt;)" style="display: none;" value=""><template shadowrootmode="open" shadowrootdelegatesfocus><!----><button id="button" class="icon-button  standard " aria-label="Свернуть 0 дочерних ячеек в разделе &quot;Executive Conclusions &amp; Insights&quot; (чтобы свернуть ячейки и в других разделах этого уровня, также нажмите &lt;Shift&gt;)">
        <!--?lit$893133885$--><md-focus-ring part="focus-ring" for="button" aria-hidden="true"><template shadowrootmode="open"><!----></template></md-focus-ring>
        <!--?lit$893133885$--><md-ripple aria-hidden="true"><template shadowrootmode="open"><!----><div class="surface   "></div></template></md-ripple>
        <!--?lit$893133885$--><span class="icon"><slot></slot></span>
        <!--?lit$893133885$-->
        <!--?lit$893133885$--><span class="touch"></span>
  </button></template><md-icon aria-hidden="true"><template shadowrootmode="open"><!----><slot></slot></template>keyboard_arrow_down</md-icon></md-icon-button><h3>Executive Conclusions &amp; Insights</h3></div>
<ol>
<li><strong>Statistical Uplift:</strong> The model confirms a highly significant causal effect. Post-2005, the actual sales (black line) diverged sharply from the counterfactual prediction (blue dashed line). </li>
<li><strong>Incremental Impact:</strong> The intervention (Wii Launch) created a massive "innovation premium". While other genres followed a stable or declining path, the Sports genre achieved an <strong>incremental cumulative gain of ~150M units</strong> above the expected baseline.</li>
<li><strong>Probability of Success:</strong> The posterior probability of a causal effect is <strong>&gt;99%</strong>, indicating that the observed growth was not a result of market noise or general gaming popularity.</li>
<li><strong>Strategic Value:</strong> This approach demonstrates a scalable framework for <strong>measuring the ROI of global product launches or major economy rebalances</strong> where randomized controlled trials (A/B tests) are technically impossible.</li>
</ol>
</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>

